# Add per-workspace containerization settings

Allow workspace-level override of containerization settings.

## Requirements

- Workspace settings table/field for container config
- Override global feature flag per-workspace
- Per-workspace isolation profile selection
- Per-workspace Docker image selection

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Workspace schema has `container_config` JSONB field
- [ ] Migration adds container_config column
- [ ] `Workspace.containerization_enabled?/1` checks workspace + global flags
- [ ] API endpoint to update workspace container settings
- [ ] Workspace isolation profile stored in settings
- [ ] AgentServer reads workspace config on init
- [ ] Unit tests for workspace-level settings
